{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3292890/extras/cardreduxlogo.png?t=1737723246\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>C.A.R.D.S REDUX is a roguelike game about a war on a fictional planet (that's almost identical to ours) where you play as robot protagonist, GLUNDO. A robot with the ability to retain memory throughout it's many deaths, in hopes that one day, they can mass produce it to help win the war.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3292890/extras/await.png?t=1737723246\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>In C.A.R.D.S REDUX you can...</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Destroy other Robots designed to stop you in your tracks!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Collect Cards as you advance throughout the rooms to prepare you as the difficulty scales.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Go to Aubrey's Shop and purchase Chips, which you can allocate to one of three slots. These chips can modify how your run will go entirely!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Destroy Bosses to prove yourself worthy as the BEST war machine this planet has ever faced.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Get killed, like, a lot of times.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Unlock EVERYTHING!!! SECRETS!!! I would tell you what everything includes, but those would include secrets....</p></li></ul>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3292890/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1737723246","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3292890/page_bg_generated.jpg?t=1737723246","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3292890/3d30ed643f072f65bf3f9d5eaa840653b3985